.TH "epf_ntb_init_epc_bar" 9 "epf_ntb_init_epc_bar" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
epf_ntb_init_epc_bar \- Identify BARs to be used for each of the NTB constructs (scratchpad region, doorbell, memorywindow)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" epf_ntb_init_epc_bar
.BI "(struct epf_ntb *ntb "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ntb" 12
NTB device that facilitates communication between HOST1 and HOST2
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Wrapper to \fBepf_ntb_init_epc_bar_interface\fP to identify the free BARs
to be used for each of BAR_CONFIG, BAR_PEER_SPAD, BAR_DB_MW1, BAR_MW2,
BAR_MW3 and BAR_MW4 for all the interfaces.
